  <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/preprocess-metadata.dita" xtrc="title:1;6:10">Move metadata (move-meta-entries) and pull content into maps (mappull) </title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/preprocess-metadata.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;7:14">The <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Users/ekimber/workspace-ditaot/dita-ot-2.x/src/main/docsrc/dev_ref/preprocess-metadata.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;7:26">move-meta-entries</codeph> step pushes metadata back and forth between maps and topics. For
